34:19.257 --> 34:21.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Â®MDNM /DALE KLEIN, TEPCO Adviser:
If you
have water flowing through the
site and you

34:21.092 --> 34:26.097 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
