much more
daunting.

35:11.676 --> 35:16.014 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
LAKE BARRETT: People are
probably not going
to have access to those
buildings for more

35:16.047 --> 35:19.451 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
