not enough to
do defueling.

35:19.484 --> 35:25.156 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: And what about
the melted fuel
in the reactor cores? They
aren't even sure

35:25.190 --> 35:26.992 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
