help me in filling the colors in
these murals.

40:41.406 --> 40:43.775 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Another artist, a
very different
kind of imagery.

40:43.808 --> 40:48.579 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Waseem Al-Marzouki documents the
history of
the Syrian conflict through
intricate, large-scale

40:48.613 --> 40:55.453 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
paintings and films that depict
military and
industrial images and symbols.
