work for a two-year period.

41:04.696 --> 41:12.136 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WASEEM AL-MARZOUKI, Artist: I
was very shocked
from what I see and what we have
experienced,

41:12.170 --> 41:17.241 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
killing, displacement, torture,
all these
things happening to us. And,
yes, so, after

41:17.275 --> 41:22.680 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
