upheaval. He decided
to tell a different kind of
story, one about

42:55.072 --> 42:57.074 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Hassan, his own cousin, who
supported the
regime.

42:57.108 --> 42:59.911 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Khoo'-dur, a strong opponent,
said he was
after complexities, seeking to
understand

42:59.944 --> 43:02.280 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
