with the government.

43:02.313 --> 43:08.920 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ALI SHEIKH KHUDR, Filmmaker:
There's a lot
of people just -- they just
didn't want to

43:08.953 --> 43:16.093 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
lose the things that they have.
They didn't
want to lose their future, they
didn't want

43:16.127 --> 43:25.203 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to lose their lives, they didn't
want to lose
in the country itself. They were
very afraid.

43:25.236 --> 43:32.844 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And they stood on one side
against the other.
So, you have -- on both sides,
you have people

43:32.877 --> 43:34.612 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
