43:34.645 --> 43:38.216 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Khudr's cousin
Hassan died
in 2013 fighting for the
government. Khudr

43:38.249 --> 43:40.151 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
