43:48.359 --> 43:57.068 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ALI SHEIKH KHUDR: The first
responsibility
was for me that there should be
a film, a

43:57.101 --> 44:09.814 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
